top.description: The number of records displayed on a page.

TMV1-Filter.description:
The filter for retrieving a subset of the ECS Images Occurrences List. Include this parameter in every request that generates paginated output

Supported fields:
  * `imageId` - The  The ID of the container image

Supported operators:
* `eq` - Operator "equal to"
* `not` - Operator "not"
* `or` - Operator "or"
